{"word":"πρόθυμος","slug":"πρόθυμος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πρόθυμος</b></el> <el>(πρό-θῡμος, ον,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>ready, willing, eager, zealous</i>, <el>π. εἰμι</el>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, = <a href='S:προθυμέομαι'><el>προθυμέομαι</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic<p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> rei, <i>eager for</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>with Preps., <el>πρ. εἴς τι</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἐπί τι, πρός τι</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>4. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:— <el>τὸ πρόθυμον  προθυμία</el>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>bearing good-will, wishing well</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-μως</el>, <i>readily, zealously, actively</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>πρ. μᾶλλον ἢ φίλως</el> <i>with</i> more <i>zeal</i> than kindness, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>-ότερον</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>-ότατα</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}